category_descriptions.Unroasted Coffee Beans: Raw coffee beans that have not yet been roasted, often intended for industrial processing or roasting.
category_descriptions.Washed Arabica Coffee: Processed Arabica coffee beans that have undergone a washing process to remove the outer layers.
category_descriptions.Flavored Coffee Products: Coffee products that have been enhanced with additional flavors, often sold in retail packaging.
category_descriptions.Packaged Coffee Gifts: Coffee products packaged as gifts, often including additional items or special packaging.
